### Health check - public endpoint, no key needed (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/public/health

###

### Get accounts - no API key (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/admin/accounts

###

### Get accounts - wrong API key (expect 401)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/admin/accounts
X-API-KEY: wrong-key

###

### Get accounts - valid API key (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:8090/api/admin/accounts
X-API-KEY: secret-key-123

###

### Create account - valid API key (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/admin/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: secret-key-123

{
  "accountNumber": "12345678",
  "holderName": "Asha Patel",
  "balance": 1000.00
}

###

### Create account - no API key (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/admin/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "12345678",
  "holderName": "Asha Patel",
  "balance": 1000.00
}
